---
// src/components/Footer.astro
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900 to-blue-800 text-white py-6 mt-auto border-t border-blue-700/30">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
    <p class="text-sm font-medium">
      © {currentYear} <span class="text-yellow-300">Học Cùng Giêsu</span>
    </p>
    <p class="text-xs opacity-80 mt-1 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Dự án dữ liệu mở về các dòng tu, tu hội Công giáo tại Việt Nam.
    </p>
    <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 text-xs opacity-75 mt-2 flex-wrap">
      <a href="https://github.com/hoccunggiesu/hoccunggiesu.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-yellow-300 transition">
        <span class="inline-block mr-1">🐙</span> GitHub
      </a>
      <span>•</span>
      <a href="/LICENSE" class="hover:text-yellow-300 transition">
        📄 Giấy phép
      </a>
      <span>•</span>
      <span>GPLv3 + CC BY-SA 4.0</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>